---
title: "Slade Networks — UniFi Installation & Support, Finger Lakes NY"
description: "UniFi network installation and support for homes and small businesses in the Finger Lakes and surrounding areas in upstate NY."
navActive: home
---
{% extends "base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
  <main>

    <section class="hero">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="heroBadge">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          Trusted local installs
        </div>
        <h1>Wi-Fi, Cameras, and Phone Systems for the Finger Lakes</h1>
        <p class="subtext">
          We install and support UniFi networks for homes and small businesses — and stay available after the job is done.
        </p>
        <div class="heroButtons">
          <a class="btn primary" href="/contact/">Request a free consultation</a>
          <a class="btn" href="/services/">See services</a>
        </div>

        <div class="trustBar">
          <div class="trustItem">
            <div class="trustIcon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
            </div>
            Cisco CCNA certified
          </div>
          <div class="trustItem">
            <div class="trustIcon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
            </div>
            CS degree, St. Bonaventure
          </div>
          <div class="trustItem">
            <div class="trustIcon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
            </div>
            Based in Penn Yan, NY
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section reveal">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sectionLabel">Recent work</p>
        <h2 class="sectionTitle">Real installs, locally done</h2>
        <p class="sectionIntro">
          Photos from real projects across the Finger Lakes region.
        </p>

        <div class="scrollWrapper" aria-label="Install photos carousel">
          <div class="productScroll">
            <div class="tile"><div class="media"><img src="/assets/IMG_0465.jpeg" alt="Wi-Fi access point installation"></div></div>
            <div class="tile"><div class="media"><img src="/assets/camera-install.jpeg" alt="Camera installation"></div></div>
            <div class="tile"><div class="media"><img src="/assets/IMG_0464.jpeg" alt="VoIP phone installation"></div></div>
            <div class="tile"><div class="media"><img src="/assets/IMG_0431.jpeg" alt="Network rack installation"></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonialSection reveal">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="testimonialCard">
          <span class="quoteMark" aria-hidden="true">&ldquo;</span>
          <p class="quoteText">His professionalism and calm, practical problem-solving ability were consistently impressive. His work has had a meaningful impact on the Museum's operations and visitor experience.</p>
          <p class="quoteAttrib">&mdash; The Finger Lakes Boating Museum</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section sectionAlt reveal">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sectionLabel">Why UniFi</p>
        <h2 class="sectionTitle">One platform. Everything connected.</h2>
        <p class="sectionIntro sectionIntroFull">
          UniFi brings Wi-Fi, cameras, and phones into one platform. Less to manage, more visibility, and a setup that stays reliable over time.
        </p>

        <div class="gridTwo reveal-stagger">
          <div class="infoCard">
            <div class="cardIcon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Everything in one place</h3>
            <p>Wi-Fi, cameras, and phones all run through a single app — no juggling three different systems from three different vendors.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="infoCard">
            <div class="cardIcon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Stays stable</h3>
            <p>Systems are configured to minimize surprises. Updates are managed so nothing breaks at a bad time.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="infoCard">
            <div class="cardIcon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12.55a11 11 0 0 1 14.08 0"/><path d="M1.42 9a16 16 0 0 1 21.16 0"/><path d="M8.53 16.11a6 6 0 0 1 6.95 0"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12.01" y2="20"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Coverage where you need it</h3>
            <p>Access points are placed and tuned for your actual space — not just plugged in wherever is convenient.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="infoCard">
            <div class="cardIcon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Support doesn't stop at handoff</h3>
            <p>Ongoing support plans include remote monitoring, firmware updates, and someone to call when something needs attention. <a href="/services/" style="color:var(--primary); font-weight:600">Learn more &rarr;</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section reveal">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sectionLabel">Location</p>
        <h2 class="sectionTitle">Service Area</h2>
        <p class="sectionIntro">Local installs across the Finger Lakes and nearby towns.</p>

        <div class="serviceAreaWrap">
          <div class="serviceAreaSquare serviceAreaCard">
            <h3>Based in Penn Yan</h3>
            <p>
              We serve homes and businesses across the Finger Lakes — Penn Yan,
              Keuka Park, Hammondsport, Watkins Glen, Geneva, Canandaigua, Naples,
              Victor, and Auburn. Ithaca and surrounding areas on a case-by-case basis.
            </p>
            <p>
              Not on the list? Reach out — for the right project, travel isn't a problem.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="serviceAreaSquare serviceAreaMap">
            <img src="/assets/service-area-map.png" alt="Slade Networks service area map in the Finger Lakes">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ctaSection reveal">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="ctaInner">
          <div>
            <h2>Start with a free on-site consultation</h2>
            <p>We come to you, walk the space, and put together a written quote — no commitment required.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="ctaButtons">
            <a class="btn primary" href="/contact/">Request a free consultation</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
{% endblock %}
